29:19.560 --> 29:20.891
You okay, buddy?

29:21.040 --> 29:23.361
You know I hate English, okay?

29:23.520 --> 29:24.601
Yeah, fine, look.

29:24.760 --> 29:27.366
(IN SPANISH) We're waiting for you.
