the famous Nefertiti.

30:18.240 --> 30:20.971
(IN ENGLISH)
Mm. Ready?

30:21.120 --> 30:22.724
(IN SPANISH)
Are you ready?

30:23.240 --> 30:24.765
Tell her I am.

30:25.760 --> 30:27.410
(IN ENGLISH)
He's ready.

30:27.560 --> 30:31.201
