38:10.680 --> 38:12.682
Everybody loved Johnny.

38:12.840 --> 38:15.525
- Because he had...
- A big heart!

38:16.360 --> 38:17.361
No.

38:17.600 --> 38:21.844
He had a big pimple on his nose
that looked really funny.

38:22.000 --> 38:23.206
(BOTH CHUCKLE)

38:23.400 --> 38:27.121
