Tell me the story right.

38:28.200 --> 38:29.247
Okay.

38:29.680 --> 38:31.489
When I was a kid...

38:32.360 --> 38:34.249
...one day, your grandpa...

38:34.400 --> 38:37.404
...threw me from the top
of La Quebrada.

38:37.600 --> 38:39.648
- Ha, ha.
- Don't laugh.

38:40.200 --> 38:41.486
I'm serious.

38:41.880 --> 38:43.405
