38:59.360 --> 39:02.842
...when will you take me to Acapulco
to jump from La Quebrada?

39:03.200 --> 39:04.247
No.

39:04.720 --> 39:06.563
I'd never do that to you.

39:06.720 --> 39:11.282
Come on, please. I don't want
to be scared of anything.

39:16.120 --> 39:17.121
(SPITTING)

39:17.280 --> 39:19.203
VALENTIN:
Good shot!

39:22.120 --> 39:23.121
