39:23.280 --> 39:24.281
(IN ENGLISH)
Yes!

39:24.440 --> 39:25.566
(IN SPANISH)
Good shot!

39:25.720 --> 39:28.246
- Very good.
- Your turn. Ahem.

39:28.400 --> 39:30.402
(COUGHS THEN CHUCKLES)

39:31.280 --> 39:34.887
- Dad, it's your turn.
- Coming. Take my turn.

39:36.040 --> 39:38.042
(MAGGIE SPITTING)

39:41.800 --> 39:43.450
