40:03.280 --> 40:04.611
MAGGIE:
"Dear Maggie...

40:04.760 --> 40:07.286
<i>...I've been too busy to come
and see you,</i>

40:07.440 --> 40:09.602
<i>'cause I've saving the world.</i>

40:09.800 --> 40:13.691
<i>On my way home,
