40:13.840 --> 40:16.844
<i>And that was when,
a mysterious masked man...</i>

40:17.000 --> 40:19.651
<i>...dressed as a bat,
asked me to help him...</i>

40:19.800 --> 40:23.122
<i>He wanted me to help
hand out bean tacos...</i>

40:23.280 --> 40:26.363
<i>...and cactus juice
to the earthquake victims...</i>

40:26.520 --> 40:28.249
<i>...in Gotham City."</i>

40:28.520 --> 40:31.330
I bet that masked man was Batman!

40:31.480 --> 40:33.642
