What else does it say?

40:33.800 --> 40:37.009
<i>"After that, I was sent on
a mission in Australia.</i>

40:38.360 --> 40:42.524
<i>I had to save the last duck-billed
platypuses from extinction.</i>

40:42.720 --> 40:46.361
<i>The mommy platypus fell in love
with a Canadian beaver...</i>

40:46.720 --> 40:47.881
<i>...much younger than she was...</i>

40:48.040 --> 40:52.170
<i>...and the tease ran off with him,
